    <title>Software Component (Partner Demo Development Tenant) Multitenancy SaaS Application</title>
    <updated>2025-01-08T12:26:09.040000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Abdurrezzak</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1913252</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hello Dear Experts,&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;I am trying to create a software component to develop multitenant SaaS products in the partner demo development system. However, I get an error like the one below.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;SCLM(Software Component Lifecycle Management) application is not configured in the current business tenant&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Abdurrezzak_1-1736334546444.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/209596iD5339B1549D83BFE/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Abdurrezzak_1-1736334546444.png" alt="Abdurrezzak_1-1736334546444.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A title="https://userapps.support.sap.com/sap/support/knowledge/en/3530333" href="https://userapps.support.sap.com/sap/support/knowledge/en/3530333" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"&gt;https://userapps.support.sap.com/sap/support/knowledge/en/3530333&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;I&gt;Resolution&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;I&gt;TDD system (Partner Demo Development Tenant) is being used and in this tenant only predefined Software Components exist and other software components cannot be created:&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;I&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;I&gt;Software Component ZPARTNER =&amp;gt; Multi-Off Development&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;I&gt;Software Component ZLOCAL =&amp;gt; System Local Development which can not be transported or deployed&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;This is what SAP said about the error. In this case, we seem to be unable to create a software component, but is there a different way we can proceed? I wanted to ask you about something that can be done to create a software component.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Or do we need a different partner system so that we can create software components for our developments?&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;If we create a development package with the namespace we have previously registered in our partner development system and develop it with the ZPARTNER software component, will we have problems in the future when offering this product as a multitenant SaaS application? How should we proceed?&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;Reasons for Necessity:&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Abdurrezzak_2-1736334659097.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/209597i9CDB5F23D5B9A7CE/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Abdurrezzak_2-1736334659097.png" alt="Abdurrezzak_2-1736334659097.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Abdurrezzak_3-1736334663162.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/209598i0B5202D0F340A483/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Abdurrezzak_3-1736334663162.png" alt="Abdurrezzak_3-1736334663162.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Abdurrezzak_4-1736334667271.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/209599iA72FD9E436981861/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Abdurrezzak_4-1736334667271.png" alt="Abdurrezzak_4-1736334667271.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Abdurrezzak_5-1736334670630.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/209600iFED226AED9AD1ABC/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Abdurrezzak_5-1736334670630.png" alt="Abdurrezzak_5-1736334670630.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Dear&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/4296"&gt;@FrankJentsch&lt;/a&gt;, your valuable comments and suggestions will make a great contribution. Thank you very much for your support.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/software-component-partner-demo-development-tenant-multitenancy-saas/qaq-p/13980321"/>
